{"tid":2142100,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"FC橫濱今季首次派出53歲三浦知良正選披甲日本聯賽盃","createTime":"2020-08-06T07:32:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T08:38:03.000Z","uid":173952,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8ce4dd0fac614af54b74eb553e21dec9f3d0f676","tid":2142100,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T07:32:55.000Z","msg":"日本聯賽盃今晚（5日）復賽，FC橫濱今季首次派出53歲球壇「長青樹」三浦知良正選披甲，刷新由自己保持的日本職業賽最年長上陣紀錄。球隊終在完場前憑中場瀨沼優司絕殺，作客以1：0小勝鳥栖砂岩，在C組1勝1負暫居第3。<br />\n<br />\n三浦知良今季隨FC橫濱重返日職，惟一直未曾在聯賽入選出場名單，今晚終在日聯盃列陣為球隊掛帥，以53歲5個月又10日之齡，刷新日本職業賽最年長上陣紀錄。三浦雖久疏戰陣，但表現不下於一眾後輩，在上半場末段更有一次插水式頭槌頂中門，最終他戰至63分鐘被換出。球隊則在補時階段，憑中場瀨沼優司射入絕殺，作客以1：0小勝鳥栖砂岩，在C組1勝1負得3分暫居第3。同組的北海道札幌岡薩多則在主場以2：1擊敗廣島三箭，兩戰全勝續居首。<br />\n<br />\n另外，日乙球會FC琉球後衛知念哲矢，於新冠病毒肺炎檢測呈陽性，是該聯賽近日第2宗球員確診個案。"},{"pid":"96d66f1bfbc21ddc2a44e66c4b4c25b8f51e6ab3","tid":2142100,"uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T07:33:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1yAXMza.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1yAXMza.png&h=58a8cde8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bcd2914b944579c650a116cb9ff66a769450ca4e","tid":2142100,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T07:34:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TM_SJooiv3Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTM_SJooiv3Y&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOhnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=e6fc85c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TM_SJooiv3Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8b3f96c3a2a5ed3551f76327a7b4f293cdf81ea","tid":2142100,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T07:36:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bSfcs-m3njY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbSfcs-m3njY&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOhnxOJLX742